[DhtmlXQ_comment6_26]不如改走马8进6，见变例。[/DhtmlXQ_comment6_26]
[DhtmlXQ_comment6_43]红方多兵占优。[/DhtmlXQ_comment6_43]
[DhtmlXQ_comment7_32]如误走炮3进1，则车三退一，炮3退1，马六进四，红方胜势。[/DhtmlXQ_comment7_32]
[DhtmlXQ_comment7_36]黑可抗衡。[/DhtmlXQ_comment7_36]
[DhtmlXQ_comment8_15]挺七兵制马，稳健的走法。[/DhtmlXQ_comment8_15]
